      • execute

        public boolean execute()
        Execute the lookup action from a given random node which is not sybil. The action is done several time to collect an estimate about how many messages we send in order to get the key associated value.
        Specified by:
        execute in interface peersim.core.Control
        Overrides:
        execute in class WhanauSetup
        Returns:
        this method returns always false.

      • lookup

        public LookupResult lookup(peersim.core.Node u,
                           int key)
        Lookup for a key from a given node (it try do do that for 15 times using also random walk sampling).
        Parameters:
        u - the given starting node
        key - the given key we are searching
        Returns:
